      '**4. Sebutkan Gaya Seni Abstrak:** Jika Anda memiliki gaya tertentu dalam pikiran, sebutkan. `An abstract oil painting in the style of Wassily Kandinsky, focusing on geometric harmony and chaotic color`, atau `a minimalist abstract sculpture in the style of Constantin BrÃ¢n-cu-È™i, smooth, clean lines, organic form`.',
